records.name: Ganduvaru Villa

descriptions.hotel: Make yourself at home in one of the 6 air-conditioned guestrooms. Rooms have private patios. Complimentary wireless internet access is available to keep you connected. Bathrooms feature showers, complimentary toiletries, and hair dryers.
descriptions.direction: With a stay at Ganduvaru Villa in Ukulhas, you'll be just steps from Ari Atoll and Ukulhas Beach. This spa hotel is 0.4 mi (0.6 km) from Ukulhas Harbor and 9.9 mi (15.9 km) from Mathiveri Ferry Terminal.
descriptions.general: Located in Ukulhas and with Ukulhas Beach reachable within a few steps, Ganduvaru Villa provides express check-in and check-out, non-smoking rooms, a garden, free WiFi throughout the property and a shared lounge. This 3-star hotel offers a tour desk. The property has room service, an ATM and currency exchange for guests. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a closet, an electric tea pot, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a patio and a private bathroom with a shower. The daily breakfast offers buffet, à la carte or continental options. Guests at Ganduvaru Villa will be able to enjoy activities in and around Ukulhas, like snorkeling.
descriptions.other: Relax at the full-service spa, where you can enjoy massages and body treatments. Additional amenities at this hotel include concierge services and a fireplace in the lobby.
